age is critical for the study of that 300 years of history in China. %0a%3c %0a%3c Reports on revitalization efforts of the Manchu Language:%0a%3c 1. Plans to save ‘critically endangered’ Manchu language are spreading to preserve ethnic culture (https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=X1eeAGr-jzs)%0a%3c 2. Saving the Manchu Language (https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nCFG-cbQOJc)%0a%3c 3. Cultural inheritor opens classes to save endangered Manchu language (https://www.globaltimes.cn/content/1172117.shtml)%0a%3c %0a%3c %0a%3c %0a%3c [[#contentends]]%0a%3c ----%0a%3c (:Category:)%0a\ No newline at end of file%0a
